title: Wen Notcoin listing? MetalCore beta & more: Web3 Gamer
description:
MetalCore says optimism, regulations behind big game release delays, NotCoin token listing speculation, Heroes of Mavia review: Web3 Gamer.

Notcoin where players just click on an animated coin to mine a crypto that’s not even out yet has roped in millions and millions of players in less than a month since it dropped. Sasha Plotvinov, founder of Notcoin devs OpenBuilders, isnt sure why, but he has some ideas.

I’d put it down to its viral and simple mechanics that encourage users to invite their crypto ‘frens’ from Telegram messenger, Plotvinov tells Web3 Gamer.

I think that fun should be paramount. Thats why Notcoin gained millions of players, even before the token announcement, he says.
